/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a low angle, looking up towards the sky, giving a sense of grandeur to the scene. The street is lined with lush green trees, providing a stark contrast to the clear blue sky. Buildings of various sizes and designs flank the street, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. Cars of different colors are seen driving on the road, adding a dynamic element to the otherwise static urban landscape. Overhead, power lines crisscross the sky, a common sight in many cities. The image is bathed in the warm glow of the sun, casting long shadows and highlighting the textures of the buildings and trees.
